title: Stargate SG1 Season 8 Disk 1 of 5
description:
NTSC, 16:9 widescreen format in a iso file of the DVD from the box set. Mount it or burn it then watch it or sleep thru it. It is all there with menus ect.and this season they include the directors commentary and a few cheesy bonus features or specials. Season 8 brings alternate language tracks and subtitles and more cheezy bonuses.. I'm trying every few days to uplaod another DVD.. So far so good.
Any problems kindly keep them to yourself or ask someone who can help
